Pre-Game Insights: Warriors' Head Coach, Collin Benjamin is preparing the team for the upcoming 2026 FIFA World Cup Qualifiers against Liberia and Tunisia.
Benjamin mentioned that the camp in Johannesburg has been competitive and the players have shown great skill and dedication.
Miscellaneous Highlights: Namibia played to a one all draw against Lesotho in a preparatory match on Saturday.
Others: Erastus Kalula scored the goal for Namibia on his national team debut.
Namibia's Match Day 3 & 4 Fixtures: Wednesday, 05 June (vs Liberia) and Sunday, 09 June (vs Tunisia) at the Orlando Stadium.
